Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.04,0:01:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和小大要去参加自治会的预算会议
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.64,0:01:37.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.67,0:01:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回来之前 这些就拜托你们收拾掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.47,0:01:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 小大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.48,0:01:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要快点出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被这样拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些大部分都是前辈们的私人物品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.69,0:01:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点说明萤一被大家信赖着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕只是觉得很麻烦而已
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.24,0:01:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这些要怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈们用微妙的平衡堆起来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微动一下的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.18,0:02:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:19.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 长谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.75,0:02:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用没有哪里受伤了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.93,0:02:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你的身后…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.26,0:02:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人没有受伤真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.35,0:02:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.97,0:02:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.81,0:02:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用客气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定是那个人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:03:00.00,Chapter,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HFFA8D3&}{\3c&H00D5D5&}啊啊 那就是嫉妒！？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（今天的实验项目：セラミック冲击实验）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（セラミック（CERAMIC）：\N一般用与代替金属的耐热陶瓷 多用与引擎）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.35,0:03:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去吃午饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:10.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然熔炉的温度没有安定下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.18,0:03:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,强度应该不是那个样子的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不经历失败 是不会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从经历失败后得到的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会提高成功的几率
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了便当后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.84,0:03:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提起精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.23,0:03:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电子科一年生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神原志穂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.89,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不认识哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然给你这样的信 十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.09,0:03:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一眼见到你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸中就有种非常奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想说出来却无法传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天鼓起勇气想向你传达
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.17,0:04:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的情书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然自己写过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到能收到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,写信的人已经把心意传达到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在喷泉前等待着你的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管多久
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.96,0:04:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 要交往吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.02,0:04:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.41,0:04:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据我的占卜好象是个非常可爱的女孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.46,0:04:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.07,0:04:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么回复呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.68,0:04:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是要交往 只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.29,0:05:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.76,0:05:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要传达心意是需要很大的能量的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好好答复是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望你偶尔也吃点醋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.55,0:05:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果决定了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.88,0:05:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快去给她回复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.60,0:05:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.34,0:05:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好给人家回复哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说这话的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的眼神是很认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.90,0:05:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 连这种情况也没有半点嫉妒的她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.75,0:05:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的相信着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.89,0:05:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 我根本就不值得去嫉妒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 果然是个可爱的女孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.10,0:06:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么说也 不可能连续有这么好的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:16.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里明明暗爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你喜欢的类型吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.61,0:06:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你胡说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.01,0:06:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂怎么看？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.93,0:06:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个很不错的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象是在找人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.36,0:06:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好象察觉到我们这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为你不会来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是这个女孩子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向我露出这么天真的微笑的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常高兴能收到你的信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.36,0:06:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:57.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能对你的感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持这样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.21,0:07:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被什么东西附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从你身上冒出了不属于人类的波动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.20,0:07:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道女神的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我的力量把恶灵赶回黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是想象一下就让人激动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶灵是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.94,0:07:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请放心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会把你身上的附着的恶灵驱除的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是退灵师之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.21,0:07:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远程教育2年生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（什么啊 外行啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 我来帮你驱除
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太罗嗦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还在磨蹭什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要甩就快点甩掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 刚才还让我去交往的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是捉弄你而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你带来疾病的女恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是恶灵而是冤魂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.65,0:08:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一曾经说过
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.54,0:08:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我陪伴在他身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不论发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都相信萤一说的那句话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太累了…我放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.50,0:08:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.65,0:08:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就开始做准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要偷窥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.74,0:08:56.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把我的房间给那个来历不明的女人用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.95,0:08:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为说方位好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么方位？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驱除恶灵的方位
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没人的走廊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传来啪蹋啪蹋的脚步声
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…都是因为我犹豫不决才会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.04,0:09:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有点担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.83,0:09:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那个女孩子喜欢萤一的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会让她留下悲伤的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我一厢情愿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:55.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.21,0:09:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个打扮是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:09:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.55,0:10:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始迎合呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太近了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.90,0:10:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵异现象？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.24,0:10:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了呢 恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 尽管放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是什么姿势啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.69,0:10:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.44,0:10:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个只会吸引低级恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是碰上这样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.10,0:11:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.63,0:11:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.49,0:11:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我来把符文拿下来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.41,0:11:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 我的符文起到作用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.01,0:11:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然有这方面的才能
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一个陪我做到最后的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.56,0:11:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你的眼神太认真了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拒绝都拒绝不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是我选择前辈的原因哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不讨厌这样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.17,0:11:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.13,0:12:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.09,0:12:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是对我下的挑战书
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点害怕 但没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.11,0:12:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次一定将它们全都的退治掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然接下来要用的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.90,0:13:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近才刚刚学会 一定会起到很好的效果的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:12.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我这个天才
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.90,0:13:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都能解决
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力量溢出？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.08,0:13:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和蓓儿丹蒂呆一起多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.20,0:13:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫉妒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.16,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂不是人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.50,0:13:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然会有这样的感情了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.51,0:13:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是女神…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.89,0:13:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能有这样的感情？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上一个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不全都是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为是女神
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.53,0:14:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才会觉得痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂她…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次发现自己有着嫉妒心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不知道该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.27,0:14:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一切都封闭在自己内心里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这么做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.15,0:14:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就会爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.52,0:14:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.36,0:14:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口像火烧一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法抑制这种黑暗的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来帮帮我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.79,0:15:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在这里就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果一个人的话就更害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.79,0:15:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然事情变成这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不打算这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我没说清楚才会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以蓓儿丹蒂不用责怪自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.07,0:15:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈请安静下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.29,0:15:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.19,0:15:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱，抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 好黑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.60,0:16:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的不要紧吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.74,0:16:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不知道这个半调子咒语是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召唤出KUDARINI…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾名为加鲁姆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃冥界的看门犬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.92,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召唤者 说出你的愿望目的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.19,0:16:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了个麻烦的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.28,0:16:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有召唤你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.58,0:16:52.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么事就召唤我加鲁姆吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说过了 没想召唤你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此罪当万死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诗寇蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.66,0:17:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点擦掉魔法阵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用魔术笔写的擦不掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就将它改写为退魔程序吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.58,0:17:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会那种公式啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔程序起不了作用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用退去系统的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.14,0:17:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抽不住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂 由你来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.71,0:17:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.84,0:17:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.97,0:17:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.56,0:17:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.45,0:18:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.09,0:18:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.32,0:18:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.38,0:18:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.16,0:18:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.99,0:18:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那个是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.91,0:18:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂所积累的嫉妒的能量\N终于不堪重负的爆发出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被这个力量直接击中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.98,0:18:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加鲁姆也会被打回去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.50,0:18:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.86,0:18:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微要动点粗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还请你原谅了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 前辈 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.75,0:19:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘术
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.51,0:19:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人体远距离操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.29,0:19:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:19.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.46,0:19:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.74,0:20:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然害怕那个女孩子会伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是更加害怕会失去萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.00,0:20:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说相信萤一的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一 你一定很讨厌我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.69,0:20:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该道歉的应该是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辜负了你对我的信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兀儿德也说过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢上一个人并不都只有好事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.35,0:20:47.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生气 哭泣 欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.09,0:20:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使这样还想在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.67,0:20:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是喜欢上一个人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.80,0:21:15.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓓儿丹蒂…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.12,0:21:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是自己操纵的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.60,0:21:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种刺痒痒的感觉到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.23,0:21:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我果然是天才 终于得到了证明
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（等等 我的房间变成这样了）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.99,0:21:39.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用这种力量使大家幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（真是的 听我说啊）
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.20,0:21:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是误打误撞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.36,0:21:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把加鲁姆召唤出来也算是天才了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.23,0:21:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.96,0:21:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢参与我这个天才的研究吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.02,0:21:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赖皮 自信狂 没有经验 自不量力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2个人很像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要说天才的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要像我这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.43,0:22:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么样的天才
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.36,0:22:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.56,0:23:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一次打错电话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.60,0:24:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和蔷薇的芳香一起出现在他面前的她
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕着短暂的再会
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.20,0:24:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 啊啊 将你的愿望实现
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.48,0:24:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你的服务是天上界第一的
